					Chronic Care and Population Health Company Persivia Acquires Alere Analytics to Help Healthcare Organizations Manage Clinical and Financial Outcomes Risk			<meta itemprop="url" content="http://52.21.11.8/news-events/256-chronic-care-and-population-health-company-persivia-acquires-alere-analytics-to-help-healthcare-organizations-manage-clinical-and-financial-outcomes-risk" />
